title: AI will probably force you to gate your content
description: On the scale of fan to skeptic to hater, when it comes to emerging AI tech like large language models and agentic coding, I’ve traditionally been very much in the middle — fascinated by the potential technical benefits, but often feeling it’s bubbly and over-emphasized.
